  "texts": [
    "Thus, adaptations should minimally affect its structure or be very well justified and validated.",
    "Otherwise, such adaptations may raise several side effects that are hard to understand.",
    "There is a huge amount of knowledge codified in the health datasets (e.g., EHRs), derived from the experience of a large number of experts for several years.",
    "As we show in this paper, current transformer models rely on such knowledge to make conclusions that are impossible or very hard to derive by humans due to the amount and complexity of relations involved.",
    "The approaches discussed in this review try to demonstrate a future where this ability can be leveraged accurately as a decision-support tool for healthcare experts."
